{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataOutputStreamRef\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"write","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"buffer"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is 0, returns 0 and does nothing. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"larger than ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0)."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"was cancelled, the error ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be returned. If an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"text":" is set accordingly.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to write "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" into the stream. Will block"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"during the operation.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataOutputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataOutputStreamRef\/OutputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE5write6buffer5count11cancellableSiSvSg_SiAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO19DataOutputStreamRefV","role":"symbol","title":"write(buffer:count:c